1034
01:06:06.935 --> 01:06:08.268
Jesus! You're overcautious.

1035
01:06:10.103 --> 01:06:11.472
Here.

1036
01:06:11.606 --> 01:06:13.675
Take the 72 North.
You'll be there in 20 minutes.

1037
01:06:13.808 --> 01:06:15.743
