what the fungus can do?

1257
01:17:03.057 --> 01:17:04.692
You're gonna kill everybody
in eastern Kansas. man!

1258
01:17:04.825 --> 01:17:06.595
We're not
killing anyone.

1259
01:17:06.760 --> 01:17:09.497
Detonation will be hundreds
of feet underground.

1260
01:17:09.630 --> 01:17:12.166
This immediate area
